description.text: This is an RTI project that has been fully approved and consists of a Co-Share Unit housing development with 24 units located in the bustling heart of Los Angeles. The property is delivered vacant, presenting an attractive investment opportunity for developers and investors seeking high-income producing Co-Share Unit Housing. Co-Share Unit Housing has rapidly gained popularity and proven to be a successful model, outpacing previous investments in condos and multi-unit properties, especially in the fast-paced housing market of Los Angeles. With its unique community living approach, Co-Share Unit Housing is an ideal solution for short-term housing needs in the area. Contact LA1 for more details.

description.text: Built in 1917, 235 N. St. Andrews Place is a charming California Craftsman Bungalow featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, with plenty of upgrades throughout. Complete with Carrera marble countertops and Fisher & Paykel appliances, the kitchen leads into a cheery breakfast nook that doubles as an office. An original glass sliding pocket door separates the cozy living room and the beautiful wood-paneled dining room with built-in China hutch. French doors open up to a patio with a view of a deep backyard, drought-tolerant landscaping, mature citrus trees, and a magnificent California Pepper tree. A newly finished ADU maintains the carriage facade of the original garage. Inside has everything you need to either work from home or welcome guests including kitchenette, laundry room, full bath, AC/Heat, and lots of storage! ADU brings an additional 550 square feet!

description.text: This one has it all! This charming 1920s home has been re-imagined with a spacious open floor plan for the modern family. Plus, it is a rare and special offering! Ideally sited behind mature landscaping, this 4 bedroom 3 bath, open floor plan home is a tucked away sanctuary offering a perfect blend of light and bright spaces with warm and thoughtful details. Completely reimagined and updated for today's living, you'll find a perfectly appointed chef's kitchen, windows that capture light all day long, and sliding doors that maximize indoor/outdoor living. Stunning backyard which features a sparkling pool, landscaping, plenty of lounging space. The primary suite features a large walk-in closet; bathroom with double vanity and quartz countertops throughout, and private balcony.
